\newlabel{tab:image_detection}{{3}{5}{Detection performance of LLMs on improper ASCII content using \textbf {image} input. Metrics are defined as in Table~\ref {tab:text_detection}. \textbf {[PLACEHOLDER: fill in values from results]}}{table.caption.13}{}}
